**Abstract:**
Essay dated July 29, 1991, from Chantilly project. Titled "The God of Philosophers and the God of Faith." Argues for radical difference between God of philosophy and God of Christian faith. Traces separation to 13th century when Christian thinkers encountered Aristotle and began understanding faith in Aristotelian categories. Engages Hans Frei's *Eclipse of Biblical Narrative*.

